msgstr "你可以通过点击场景列表中的 *添加新的* 按钮，添加一个新的场景.当你创建一个新的场景, 有以下的一些选项："

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:31
msgid "Add scene pop-up menu."
msgstr "添加场景的弹出菜单。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:34
msgid "New"
msgstr "新建"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:35
msgid "Creates an empty scene with default values."
msgstr "使用默认值新建一个空的场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:38
msgid "Copy Settings"
msgstr "拷贝设置"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:37
msgid ""
"Creates an empty scene but also copies the settings from the active scene"
" into the new one."
msgstr "使用当前活动场景的新建一个场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:45
msgid "Link Objects"
msgstr "链接物体"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:41
msgid ""
"This option creates a new scene with the same settings and contents as "
"the active scene. However, instead of copying the objects, the new scene "
"contains links to the objects in the old scene. Therefore, changes to "
"objects in the new scene will result in the same changes to the original "
"scene, because the objects used are literally the same. The reverse is "
"also true."
msgstr "此选项会创建一个新的场景使用活动场景的设置和内容。然而，与拷贝设置的区别是，新场景的物体都是链接于旧场景的。因此，新场景中物体的改动都会对旧场景产生相同的改动，因为所使用的对象是如同字面是相同的，反过来也是如此。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:56
msgid "Link Object Data"
msgstr "链接物体数据"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:48
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Creates new, duplicate copies of all of the objects in the currently "
"selected scene, but each one of those duplicate objects will have links "
"to the object-data (meshes, materials and so on) of the corresponding "
"objects in the original scene."
msgstr "在当前选中的场景中创建所有对象的副本，但是每个副本将拥有原场景对应的 object-data 的链接（网格, 材质等等）。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:52
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This means that you can change the position, orientation and size of the "
"objects in the new scene without affecting other scenes, but any "
"modifications to the object-data (meshes, materials, etc.) will also "
"affect other scenes. This is because a single instance of the \"object-"
"data\" is now being shared by all of the objects in all of the scenes, "
"that link to it. This has the effect of making a new independent copy of "
"the object-data."
msgstr ""
"这意味着，可以改变新场景中物体的位置，方向和大小而不影响到其它场景。但是任何对物体数据（网格，材质 "
"*等*）的修改都会影响到其它场景。这是因为所有的场景都是链接的一份 *单例物体数据* 。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:61
msgid "Full Copy"
msgstr "完整复制"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Using this option, nothing is shared. This option creates a fully "
"independent scene with copies of the active scenes contents. Every object"
" in the original scene is duplicated, and a duplicate, private copy of "
"its object-data is made as well."
msgstr "此选项会创建一个活动场景的独立拷贝，任何数据都不会共享，对象数据也是如此。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:65
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To choose between these options, it is useful to understand the "
"difference between *Objects* and *Object Data*. See :doc:`Duplication "
"</editors/3dview/transform/duplication/introduction>`."
msgstr ""
"在这些选项中选择，有助于理解物体和物体数据之间的不同。详见：doc:`复制 "
"</editors/3dview/transform/duplication/introduction>`."

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:69
msgid ""
"The choices for adding a scene, therefore, determine just how much of "
"this information will be *copied from* the active scene to the new one, "
"and how much will be *shared* (linked)."
msgstr "选择增加场景的方式时，就能明确的知道那些信息会拷贝，那些信息是共享的。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:74
msgid "Removing a Scene"
msgstr "移除场景"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:76
msgid ""
"You can delete the current scene by clicking the *X* next to the name in "
"the Info Editor."
msgstr "在信息编辑器中，点击场景名字旁边的 *X* 按钮就可以把当前场景给删除了。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:82
msgid "Background Set Scene"
msgstr "设置背景场景"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:84
msgid ""
"You can use a scene as a background, this is typically useful when you "
"want to focus on animating the foreground for example, without background"
" elements getting in the way."
msgstr "可使用一个场景作为背景，例如当你专注于动画的前景，又不想背景元素碍事时，这通常很有用。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:88
msgid ""
"You can assign a *Background* to your current scene from the *Properties "
"Editor* *Scene* panel."
msgstr "你可在 *场景属性编辑器* 面板中制定一个 *背景* 给当前场景。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:90
msgid ""
"This scene can have its own animation, physics-simulations etc, but you "
"will have to select it from the *Scene* browser if you want to edit any "
"of its contents."
msgstr "这个场景有它自己的动画，物理模拟等等，注意的是编辑时需要在 *场景* 浏览器中选中。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:93
msgid ""
"This can also be used in combination with `Linking to a Scene`_, where "
"one blend-file contains the environment, which can be re-used in many "
"places."
msgstr "``.blend`` 文件如果也有环境，也可与 `链接到一个场景` 组合使用，这样就可在多处复用。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:98
msgid "Linking to a Scene"
msgstr "链接到一个场景"

#: ../../manual/data_system/scenes.rst:100
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can link any object from one scene to another. Just open the scene "
"where these objects are, from the 3D View header access "
":menuselection:`Object --> Make Links...` and choose the scene where you "
"want your objects to appear. The selected objects will be added to that "
"scene but remain linked to the original objects."
msgstr ""
"你可从一场景链接任意物体到另一场景。仅需要打开物体所在的场景，从 3D视图的菜单栏 :menuselection:`Obejct -> Make "
"Links...` 中选择你想要物体出现的场景。选择的物体就会被添加到那场景中，但任链接到原物体。"

